derivation: or תֻּשִׁיָּה; from an unused root probably meaning to substantiate;
outline:
1. wisdom, sound knowledge, success, sound or efficient wisdom, abiding success
    1. sound or efficient wisdom
    2. abiding success (of the effect of sound wisdom)
kjv_def: enterprise, that which (thing as it) is, substance, (sound) wisdom, working.
strongs_def: support or (by implication) ability, i.e. (direct) help, (in purpose) an undertaking, (intellectual) understanding
